      "textPreview": "in all your ways know him, and he will make your paths straight.",
      "crossRefLabels": [
        "Pr 11:5"
      ],
      "footnoteMarkers": []
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "textLength": 70,
      "textPreview": "Don’t be wise in your own eyes; fear the Lord and turn away from evil.",
