        "Dt 28:8",
        "Mal 3:10"
      ],
      "footnoteMarkers": []
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "textLength": 80,
      "textPreview": "Do not despise the Lord’s instruction, my son, and do not loathe his discipline;",
