        "Pr 5:11–13",
        "Pr 15:5",
        "Pr 15:31"
      ],
      "footnoteMarkers": []
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "textLength": 100,
      "textPreview": "for the Lord disciplines the one he loves, just as a father disciplines the son ",
      "crossRefLabels": [
        "Dt 8:5",
        "Jb 5:17",
        "Pr 13:24",
        "Heb 12:5–7"
      ],
      "footnoteMarkers": []
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "textLength": 63,
      "textPreview": "Happy is a man who finds wisdom and who acquires understanding,",
      "crossRefLabels": [
        "Pr 8:32",
        "Pr 8:34"
      ],
      "footnoteMarkers": []
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "textLength": 76,
      "textPreview": "for she is more profitable than silver, and her revenue is better than gold.",
