      "textPreview": "Her ways are pleasant, and all her paths, peaceful.",
      "crossRefLabels": [
        "Mt 11:19"
      ],
      "footnoteMarkers": []
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "textLength": 87,
      "textPreview": "She is a tree of life to those who embrace her, and those who hold on to her are",
