        "Pr 13:12",
        "Pr 15:4",
        "Rv 2:7"
      ],
      "footnoteMarkers": []
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "textLength": 82,
      "textPreview": "The Lord founded the earth by wisdom and established the heavens by understandin",
      "crossRefLabels": [
        "Ps 104:24",
        "Pr 8:27"
      ],
      "footnoteMarkers": []
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "textLength": 79,
      "textPreview": "By his knowledge the watery depths broke open, and the clouds dripped with dew.",
      "crossRefLabels": [
        "Gn 7:11",
