      "textPreview": "Maintain sound wisdom and discretion. My son, don’t lose sight of them.",
      "crossRefLabels": [
        "Pr 4:21"
      ],
      "footnoteMarkers": []
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "textLength": 54,
      "textPreview": "They will be life for you and adornment for your neck.",
      "crossRefLabels": [
        "Pr 4:22"
      ],
      "footnoteMarkers": [
        1,
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "textLength": 64,
      "textPreview": "Then you will go safely on your way; your foot will not stumble.",
      "crossRefLabels": [
        "Ps 91:12",
        "Pr 4:12"
      ],
      "footnoteMarkers": []
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "textLength": 94,
      "textPreview": "When you lie down, you will not be afraid; you will lie down, and your sleep wil",
